ch.hephaistos.utilities.loki.util.annotations

Annotation Type TransferMethod


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface TransferMethod
    This annotation is supposed to be used in conjunction with ReflectorGrid. It has different variables which are used to set different options during the creation of the grid. enabled() allows you to show a disabled button on the GUI. tooltip() show the user a tooltip when hovering over the button name() sets the name to be displayed in the button.       Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description

      This gives the Label of the variable a tooltip, which the user can show when hovering over it with the mouse.
